=head1 NAME

_COADD_JSA_TILES_ACSIS_ - co-add JSA tiled data cubes

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive should co-adds all the files in the frame using
a method still to be determined.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

=over 4

=item TITLE

The title for the co-added cube.

=item OUT

The output filename.

=back

